    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Under the hood lies the S65 4.0L V8, featuring a lightweight aluminum-silicon alloy crankcase, eight individual throttle bodies, and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system for precise valve timing. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline, channeled through a traditional 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN ViscoLok limited-slip differential. The chassis is factory-spec with a weight-saving carbon fiber roof and remains in concours condition. All critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been documented. This is a turn-key collector's piece with zero mechanical or aesthetic compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
