      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade specimen that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, featuring original factory paint with a deep, swirl-free luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The interior remains indistinguishable from new: the leather bolsters show zero compression or wear, the dashboard is free of any UV exposure, and it retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It has been maintained strictly according to\u2014and often ahead of\u2014the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized technicians included. Every electronic component, switch, and sensor functions perfectly. From the spotless engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh premium rubber, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle. Pre-purchase inspections are welcomed and encouraged.",
